# Decide the Stream Epoch Model

## Question

Map the observer's epoch model onto streams: what plays the session role
per source (Slack channel? thread? Front inbox? conversation? GitHub repo?
metric family?), where raw events persist as the run_chunks analog
(ClickHouse?), epoch thresholds per source (volume/quiet-gap tuned to each
medium), page schema deltas (source field vs new section; provenance =
event ids + permalinks), and the naming collision resolution (Bugle
domain-layer Observation vs observation pages — settle terminology once).
